{"id":637,"date":"2020-08-28T16:27:38","date_gmt":"2020-08-28T09:27:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=637"},"modified":"2024-10-21T14:45:20","modified_gmt":"2024-10-21T07:45:20","slug":"restaurant-nineteen","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/restaurant-nineteen\/","title":{"rendered":"Restaurant Nineteen"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Buffet-dinner-header.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/ca1e46575bf56487dd28a83fd47e7db8_Buffet-dinner-header-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/ca1e46575bf56487dd28a83fd47e7db8_Buffet-dinner-header-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/ca1e46575bf56487dd28a83fd47e7db8_Buffet-dinner-header-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/ca1e46575bf56487dd28a83fd47e7db8_Buffet-dinner-header-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Buffet-dinner-header.jpg\" alt=\"Buffet-dinner-header\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47ljlcpj fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47ljlcpk fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ljlcpp fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/f0cffd3021618b24f3a29af8a3a259c6_Nineteen-Buffet-Restaurant-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Nineteen Buffet Restaurant\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47ljlcpq fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Our flagship restaurant Nineteen, named after our address at 19 Lam Son Square, has grown a reputation in Saigon for its unparalleled seafood buffet and five-star dining experience. The seafood is caught fresh from Vietnam&rsquo;s waters in the East Sea and off the tropical holiday island of Phu Quoc in the southwest.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">But Nineteen isn&rsquo;t just about the seafood buffet. Everyday there are breakfast and lunch buffets that include the freshest and best quality produce that can be sourced in Vietnam and from abroad, including mouthwatering roasts, ribs, vegetables and salads.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Whether you prefer soup or sushi, pho or pancakes, both Asian and Western options are available for the most discerning eaters to mix things up a bit, all of course, topped off with an indulgent spread of delicious desserts.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Dinner Buffet<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* <strong>VND 1,490,000 ++<\/strong> per person <br \/>Mondays to Sundays. From 17:45 to 22:00<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Sunday Brunch<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* <strong>VND 1,490,000 ++<\/strong> per person. <br \/>Every Sunday. From 12:00 to 15:00<br \/>(*) Including soft drinks, tea and coffee<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">More beverage selections:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Gold Package: at VND 299,000++ per person<br \/>Soju, Red wines &amp; White wines, 2 cocktails of the month, beers &amp; soft-drinks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Platinum Package: at VND 399,000++ per person<br \/>Soju, Sparkling wine, Red &amp; White wines, 2 cocktails of the month, beers &amp; soft-drinks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Prices are subject to 5% Service Charge &amp; 8% VAT<br \/>For more information, please contact <a class=\"purple-link\" href=\"tel:842838234999\">(84) 2838 234 999<\/a> or email: <a class=\"purple-link\" href=\"mailto:culinary@caravellehotel.com\">culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/a><br \/>_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Standards benefits for members of Caravelle Classique Club applicable<br \/>Children and senior citizens discounts apply<br \/>(Guests need to show ID card or equivalent)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Below 6 years old: Free of charge<br \/>From 6 years old to 10 years old: 50% off<br \/>From 70 years old: 30% off, cannot be combined with other discounts or promotions<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-73051fon fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-4n949lgh buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Nineteen-Seafood-Meatlover-06-2023.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">MENU<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-73051vm4 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-73051vm5 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/best-seafood-buffet-dinner\/\" class=\"ffb-block-button-2-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">OFFER<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-7305dend fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6r3q7g4j buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/en\/nineteen-buffet-restaurant\/reserve\/message?utm_source=hotel_website\" class=\"ffb-block-button-3-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">BOOK YOUR TA